    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/1986" key="#Princeps">Sico</persName> Dei previdentia
                        Beneventane provincie <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3620"
                            >Roffrid</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">thesaurarii</rs> nostri, tibi <persName
                            key="#Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3621">Iosep</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">examiatori</rs> nostro <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ><rs key="#Landed_possessions">terram</rs> et <rs key="#Wine"
                                >vineam</rs><rs key="#Size"> modios viginti</rs></rs> quam <name
                            ref="Leo">Leo</name>, <name ref="David">David</name>, <name ref="Ioseph"
                            >Iosep</name>, <name ref="Maurus">Maurus</name>, <name ref="Allo"
                            >Allo</name>, <name ref="Lupus">Lupus</name>
                        <rs key="#Freeborn">liberi homines</rs> ab <name ref="Auculus"
                        >Auculo</name>, <name ref="Donatus">Donato</name>, <name ref="Vitalianus"
                            >Vitaliano</name>, <name ref="Lobene">Lobene</name>, <name
                            ref="Mundulus">Mundulo</name>, <name ref="Lutephanus">Lutephano</name>,
                            <name>Brettone</name>, <name ref="Maurinus">Maurino</name>, <name
                            ref="Martinus">Martino</name>, <name ref="Grasoald">Grasoaldo</name>,
                            <name ref="Iohannes">Iohanne</name>, <name ref="Ursus">Urso</name> et
                            <name ref="Petrus">Petro</name>
                        <rs key="#Slave">servi sacris nostris palatii</rs> comparaverunt, <rs
                            key="#Iudiciaria">iudiciaria</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3622" key="#Other_palatine_officer"
                            >Douferi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">maripahis</rs> nostri, in ea videlicet
                        ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum predictam
                        terram tu et heredes tui habere et possidere valeatis, et ai nullis ex
                        nostris iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldiis vel a quibuscumque agentibus
                        habeatis aliquam requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus ut superius
                        concessimus predictam terram et vineam possideatis. Quod vero preceptum
                        concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            ref="#people/3460" key="#Notary">Leo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName> in sacro <rs key="#Palatium"
                            >palatio</rs> quarto anno, mense iunio, quarta decima. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p><emph>Editions</emph>: IS1 VIII, col. 628D-629B; IS2 X-2, col. 459C-460A; CSS,
                    III, 08, pp. 493-494 (source of the text reproduced here). <emph>Document
                        summaries</emph>: Di Meo 1795-1819, III, p. 316; Poupardin 1907, Catalogue,
                    I, n. 19; Voigt 1902, 37; Bertolini P. 1968, pp. 118-119, n. 7; RIM, 592.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
                <p>Bertolini O. 1926, n. 101, p. 21.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="links">
                <p>https://digi.vatlib.it/view/MSS_Vat.lat.4939</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Il cod. Vat. lat. 4939, noto come <title>Liber preceptorum Beneventani monasterii
                        S. Sophiae</title> o, più comunemente, come <title>Chronicon S.
                        Sophiae</title>, fu redatto nello <foreign>scriptorium</foreign> del
                    monastero di S. Sofia di Benevento e terminato nell'anno 1119. Il documento è
                    emesso dal principe Sicone.</p>
            </div>
